      "author": "Rosemary1812",
      "description": "## Bug Fixes\n\n- **Multi-line selection fix**: Fixed issue where selecting a multi-line paragraph would only highlight the first line. Now each line is individually highlighted with ==...== and appended as a contiguous blockquote block.\n- **Split view fix**: Activating the plugin now correctly creates a vertical split using \\`splitActiveLeaf('vertical')\\` instead of replacing the current tab.\n- **Deduplication fix**: Consecutive blockquote lines are now joined into a single key for deduplication, matching the append format.",
